<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130873>
    dc:description "Fig. 37. Sensory structures on antenna of A) Lesteva pallipes, B–C) Lesteva pubescens, D–E) Unamis sp. undescribed, F–G) Phlaeopterus houkae, H–I) Phlaeopterus obsoletus, J–K) Phlaeopterus elongatus. In B, D, F, H, and J, white boxes indicate inset area that is magnified in the image to the right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130873/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130863>
    dc:description "Fig. 33. Epipharynges, ventral view, of A) Lesteva pallipes, B) Lesteva longoelytrata, C) Unamis sp." ;
