<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130879>
    dc:description "Fig. 41. Phlaeopterus species, hypopharynges, dorsal view, of A) P. obsoletus, B) P. kavanaughi, C) P. elongatus. D) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, metatrochanter with apical tooth. Heads, ventral view, of E) Lesteva pallipes, F) Lesteva pubescens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10130879/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10130859>
    dc:description "Fig. 31. Labra of A) Lesteva pallipes, B) Lesteva pubescens, C) Unamis sp. undescribed, D) Unamis sp., E) Phlaeopterus lagrandeuri, F) Phlaeopterus houkae, G) Phlaeopterus obsoletus, H) Phlaeopterus filicornis. White arrows indicate labrum." ;
